review_blob: A great everyday amber ale. I some toasty carmal notes rolling around in there. I wish they still bottled so I could bring this back with me.
Man The banana and clove pop in this one. Nice creamy mouth feel. On tap all over Ocean City. I have had it multiple times this week!
Just my style of IPA. I like the flavor and aroma hops additions. Not one that will take the enamel off your teeth, and just hoppy enough.
